    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine and its signature individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a tight limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis is enhanced with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the platform's legendary tactile feedback. While the car shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its 'good' status, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and compression\u2014are within factory specifications. This is an excellent opportunity for an enthusiast seeking a high-revving, naturally aspirated performance icon that is ready for the canyon roads.",
